title: [Solhaven, Conch Street]
description: Here in the shadow of Vornavis' western wall, workers unload wagons and fill carts with boxed goods.  The carts are hauled up the cliffside on metal tracks with ropes pulled by still more laborers.  Guards are posted up the cliffs as far as you can see.

Here in the shadow of Vornavis' western wall, workers unload wagons and fill carts with boxed goods.  The carts are hauled up the cliffside on metal tracks with ropes pulled by still more laborers.  Vornavian guardsmen mingle with those in Solhaven blue and silver, gathered in squads along the cliffs as far as the eye can see.
